text: Inga Paškovska (born 20 January 1992) is a cross-country skier from Latvia.FIS profile Her World Cup debut came in 2017. Inga Paškovska is set to compete for Latvia at the 2018 Winter Olympics.Pyeongchang 2018 profile == References == Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Cross-country skiers at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Latvian female cross-country skiers Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of Latvia
